// ============================================================
//  Camp Control — Display Board Firmware  (LVGL v9 / ESP32 core 3.x)
//  Target: Waveshare ESP32-S3-Touch-LCD-4.3 (800×480, GT911 touch)
//
//  Multi-screen UI:
//    STANDBY  — clock + battery % gauge (tap anywhere → BUTTONS)
//    BUTTONS  — 6 relay toggle buttons   (swipe L/R between pages)
//    MONITOR  — telemetry cards + 30-min history graph
//    LEVELING — bubble level + start-level button
//
//  Swipe left/right cycles BUTTONS → MONITOR → LEVELING.
//  Idle 30s with no touch returns to STANDBY.
//
//  Board config: esp_panel_board_supported_conf.h must be in this folder
//  with the 4.3" board enabled (already done — that's why it boots).
// ============================================================

